text: Prithvi Singh (born 29 September 1993) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Railways in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 13 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Railways cricketers
